      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a solid start. It definitely captures that 19th-century vibe. Can you expand on that? Maybe have him go into more detail about why they are fundamentally incapable of governing themselves? I want him to explain the 'scientific' reasons why these tribes need external management to avoid falling into chaos.",
